## Key Gaps vs. GEOS

- No automated miner: all 4 tasks were hand-written vs. GEOS's RST-based extraction pipeline.
- `lj_melt_minimal` has no ground truth ‚Äî can only be evaluated structurally, not with LLM judge.
- No contamination blocking: if a LAMMPS library is mounted, the agent can read the exact `.in`
  files the tasks were inspired by (no hardlink-copy sanitization equivalent).
- No `example_pairs.jsonl`: no tracking of which source `.in` file each task was derived from.
